title: Toge no Genkiya
description: Serves meat, veg options available. This is a casual little musubi (rice ball) restaurant. They have brown rice musubi with our without nori seaweed wrappings, and with many different fillings. They also have lunch sets, which are are two musubi, miso soup and some small vegetable dishes. Their soup stock is vegan, but some of the musubi fillings include fish so watch out. Also look out for the natural foods store on the sixth floor of the same building.
